∀ {P : Type u_1} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ EuclideanGeometry.lineSegment B C →
    Y ∈ EuclideanGeometry.lineSegment C A → Z ∈ EuclideanGeometry.lineSegment A B →
      (EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
         EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
           EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z)

∀ {P : Type u_1} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.Polygon P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ EuclideanGeometry.segment B C →
  Y ∈ EuclideanGeometry.segment C A →
  Z ∈ EuclideanGeometry.segment A B →
  EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
  EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
  EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.Plane P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  EuclideanGeometry.Between B X C →
    EuclideanGeometry.Between C Y A →
      EuclideanGeometry.Between A Z B →
        (EuclideanGeometry.area A Z Y ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
          EuclideanGeometry.area B X Z ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z ∨
            EuclideanGeometry.area C Y X ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area X Y Z)

∀ {P : Type u_1} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.Plane P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ LineSegment ℝ B C → Y ∈ LineSegment ℝ C A → Z ∈ LineSegment ℝ A B →
  (EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea A Z Y ≤ EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea X Y Z ∨
   EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea B X Z ≤ EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea X Y Z ∨
   EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea C Y X ≤ EuclideanGeometry.triangleArea X Y Z)

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry.affineSpace P ℝ] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ openSegment ℝ B C → Y ∈ openSegment ℝ C A → Z ∈ openSegment ℝ A B →
  min (EuclideanGeometry.area ℝ A Z Y) (min (EuclideanGeometry.area ℝ B X Z) (EuclideanGeometry.area ℝ C Y X))
  ≤ EuclideanGeometry.area ℝ X Y Z

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  (X ∈ OpenSegment P B C) → (Y ∈ OpenSegment P C A) → (Z ∈ OpenSegment P A B) → 
  (area A Z Y ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area B X Z ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area C Y X ≤ area X Y Z)

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] (A B C X Y Z : P),
  X ∈ Segment P B C → Y ∈ Segment P C A → Z ∈ Segment P A B →
  min ([TriangleArea A Z Y], [TriangleArea B X Z], [TriangleArea C Y X]) ≤ [TriangleArea X Y Z]

∀ {P : Type*} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ lineSegment B C → Y ∈ lineSegment C A → Z ∈ lineSegment A B →
  (area A Z Y ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area B X Z ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area C Y X ≤ area X Y Z)

∀ {P : Type u} [inst : EuclideanGeometry P] {A B C X Y Z : P},
  X ∈ LineSegment ℝ B C → Y ∈ LineSegment ℝ C A → Z ∈ LineSegment ℝ A B →
  let area := EuclideanGeometry.area in
  area A Z Y ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area B X Z ≤ area X Y Z ∨ area C Y X ≤ area X Y Z
